                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1"><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"><locus target="#1va">Fol. 1va</locus>-b l. 19: Note on computation of the feasts.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="IT" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 1va-b l. 19:</span></span><span lang="IT" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4768;&#4621;&#4710;&#4961; &#4768;&#4704;&#4677;&#4724;&#4961; &#4808;&#4768;&#4621;&#4710;&#4961; &#4632;&#4901;&#4677;&#4821;&#4961; &#4704;&#4614;&#4752;&#4961; &#4874;&#4828;&#4961; &#4969; &#4632;&#4901;&#4677;&#4821;&#4961; &#4635;&#4853;&#4648;&#4877;&#4961; &#4768;&#4845;&#4872;&#4707;&#4637;&#4961; &#4824;&#4845;&#4872;&#4709;&#4653;&#4961; &#4969;&#4848;&#4961; &#4632;&#4901;&#4677;&#4816;&#4961; &#4813;&#4873;&#4829;&#4961; &#4616;&#4845;&#4777;&#4757;&#4961; &#4709;&#4622;&#4961; &#4618;&#4673;&#4961; &#4768;&#4813;&#4877;&#4830;&#4723;&#4621;&#4962;</span></span><span lang="AMH" unicode="" arial="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:Nyala;mso-fareast-font-family:"> </span><span lang="IT" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in Amharic and Gǝʿǝz. It contains instructions for calculating the mobile feasts of the year.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2"><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"><locus target="#1vb">Fol. 1vb</locus>ls. 12-20: Chronological note.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p>&#160;<span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 1vb ls. 12-20:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4773;&#4637;&#4661;&#4709;&#4779;&#4725;&#4961; &#4624;&#4811;&#4653;&#4843;&#4725;&#4961; &#4773;&#4661;&#4776;&#4961; &#4632;&#4757;&#4877;&#4645;&#4720;&#4961; &#4853;&#4846;&#4677;&#4621;&#4901;&#4843;&#4758;&#4661;&#4961; &#4970;&#4987;&#4984;&#4808;&#4975;&#4819;&#4632;&#4725;&#4961; &#4773;&#4632;&#4757;&#4877;&#4645;&#4720;&#4961; &#4853;&#4846;&#4677;&#4621;&#4901;&#4843;&#4758;&#4661;&#4961; &#4982;&#4977;&#4819;&#4632;&#4725;&#4961; &#4782;&#4752;&#4961; &#4873;&#4707;&#4818;&#4961; &#4754;&#4677;&#4843;&#4961; &#4704;&#4632;&#4811;&#4821;&#4616;&#4961; &#4680;&#4661;&#4896;&#4757;&#4898;&#4758;&#4661;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;&#10;font-family:"> </span><span lang="EN-GB" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:">&#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note indicates the number of years between the preaching of the Apostles and the reign of Diocletian (277 years), between the reign of Diocletian and the Council of Nicaea (59 years), between the reign of Diocletian and the Council of Constantinople (117 years).</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3"><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"><locus target="#1vb">Fol. 1vb</locus>ls. 21-26: Chronological note.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 1vb ls. 21-26:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4704;&#4846;&#4624;&#4757;&#4661;&#4961; &#4720;&#4928;&#4752;&#4656;&#4961; &#4704;&#4635;&#4724;&#4814;&#4661;&#4961; &#4720;&#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4704;&#4617;&#4675;&#4661;&#4961; &#4720;&#4896;&#4632;&#4672;&#4961; &#4704;&#4635;&#4653;&#4678;&#4661;&#4961; &#4720;&#4656;&#4672;&#4616;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"> &#8230;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is crudely written. It indicates the years in which Jesus Christ was conceived, born, baptized and crucified.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4"><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"><locus target="#8ra">Fol. 8ra</locus>: Ownership note.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 8ra:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4824;&#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4768;&#4704;&#4624;&#4845;&#4616;&#4961; &#4634;&#4779;&#4772;&#4621;&#4962;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in red ink and is encircled in a frame in black ink. It states that ʾabba Ḥaylä Mikaʾel is the owner of the Ms.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a5"><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"><locus target="#17ra">Fol. 17ra</locus>-b: Unclear note.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;">&#160;<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 17ra:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4704;&#4661;&#4632;&#4961; &#4773;&#4877;&#4826;&#4768;&#4709;&#4628;&#4653;&#4961; &#4629;&#4843;&#4813;&#4961; &#4632;&#4624;&#4653;&#4961; &#4808;&#4632;&#4661;&#4720;&#4643;&#4613;&#4621;&#4961; &#4757;&#4812;&#4901;&#4757;&#4961; </span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4925;</span></span><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&#8230;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The biggest part of the note has been effaced. The only two legible lines have been encircled in a frame in black ink.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a6"><p>&#160;<span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; text-align: justify;"><locus target="#17rb">Fol. 17rb</locus>-vb: Note on the length of days and nights of the months.</span></p> <p style="margin-bottom: 0.0001pt; text-align: justify;" class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;&#10;font-family:"></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Fol. 17rb-vb:</span></span><span lang="EN-US" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:&#10;115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4624;&#4659;</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4709;&#4961; &#4824;&#4632;&#4819;&#4621;&#4725;&#4961; &#4808;&#4620;&#4618;&#4725;&#4961; &#4824;&#4845;&#4752;&#4813;&#4613;&#4961; &#4808;&#4840;&#4624;&#4925;&#4653;&#4961; &#4704;&#4808;&#4653;&#4739;&#4961; &#4632;&#4661;&#4776;&#4653;&#4637;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" unicode="" style="font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"> </span><span style="font-size: small;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">sic</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">)</span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;"> </span><span style="font-size: large;"><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;">&#4978;&#4808;&#4970;&#4961; &#4632;&#4819;&#4621;&#4725;&#4961; &#4808;&#4978;&#4961; &#4808;&#4970;&#4961; &#4620;&#4618;&#4725;&#4961; &#4781;&#4621;&#4772;&#4633;&#4961; &#4773;&#4649;&#4845;&#4961; &#4616;&#4808;&#4653;&#4739;&#4961; &#4901;&#4677;&#4637;&#4725;&#4961; &#4978;&#4961; &#4808;&#4969;&#4961; &#4632;&#4819;&#4621;&#4725;&#4961; &#4978;&#4961; &#4808;&#4971;&#4961; &#4620;&#4618;&#4725;&#4961;</span></span><span lang="AMH" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Nyala;"> </span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&#8230;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note indicates the number of the long and short days and nights for each month. Further computation notes are followed.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- The title ባህረ፡ ሐሳብ፡ is written on the front board with blue paint.&#xD;
- Two tables are drawn in red ink and left unfilled on fol. 18rv&#xD;
- Omitted letters or words inserted interlineally: e.g., fols. 8ra-b, 9ra-b, 11ra, 11vb, 14rb, 15r.&#xD;
- Omitted numeral added at the beginning of the line: fol. 11va.&#xD;
- Omitted numeral added at the end of the line: fol. 13ra.&#xD;
- Erasures: e.g., fols. 8va, 9rb, 10rb, 11vb.&#xD;
- Immediate corrections indicated by thin lines above and below the word: fols. 8vb, 9vb, 10rb, 14va.&#xD;
- Scribbles: fols. 12v.</item>
                     </list>
